iv></div></div></div></div><div class=\"team-header_background-icon-wrapper-copy\"><img data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"-0.25\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/6924418b395e9ab3d12cfac8_shape-2.svg\" loading=\"eager\" class=\"team-header_background-icon-copy\"></div><div data-hidden=\"live\" class=\"dark_background\"></div></header><header class=\"section_team-profile-large_header-1\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid team-profile-large_header-1_content\"><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_content-left\"><h2>Committed to delivering the best outcome for you</h2></div><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_content-right\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><p>Phil rejoined us in 2025 as a Partner and Head of our Commercial team.</p><p>‍</p><p>He specialises in commercial law and works closely with owner managed businesses and SMEs across Yorkshire and throughout the UK. Phil provides practical, commercially focused advice that helps businesses move forward.</p><p>‍</p><p>His recent work includes supporting a client with an ongoing service level agreement involving regular contract negotiations with international household brands in the services sector. He has also advised a London based business as it expands its operations and develops relationships with leading names in the entertainment sector.</p><p>‍</p><p>Alongside his legal career, Phil holds a Diploma in Management and serves as a trustee and director of Horsforth School. Outside work, he enjoys both playing and watching a wide range of sports.</p><p>‍</p><p>Phil is also recognised by The Legal 500 for his expertise in commercial law.</p><p>‍</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></header><section class=\"section_expertise-video w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"wrapper_wide-screen is