a</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Had no troubles with Phil, he&#x27;s been on time, very informative and very well priced for the amount of work he has done for me.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Commercial Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">The team at Moonstone Advocates is both friendly and professional. Its most important characteristic, however, is that it gets results and produces positive outcomes. The team works across disciplines and can therefore provide a holistic service.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Commercial Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">We needed advice on a US contract which needed to be turned around quickly and the Commercial team at Moonstone did that for us. They turned this around incredibly promptly, without any fuss and supported our contract review at a fair price – I highly recommend them!</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Commercial Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">We have in the main used the commercial team which we would highly recommend but on occasion we have been referred to other areas of the team and the service has been of a similarly high level.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Legal 500</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">The team at Moonstone Advocates stands out for their meticulous attention to detail, commercial awareness, and client centric approach. They demonstrated a deep understanding of the complexities involved in our transaction, ensuring a smooth and efficient due diligence process.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Legal 500</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><section class=\"section_cta17\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"wrapper_wide-screen padding-0\"><div class=\"cta17_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid cta17_content\"><div class=\"cta17_content-left\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div data-scroll-speed=\"0.025\" data-scroll=\"\" class=\"dynamic-heading_component\"><h2 class=\"heading-style-h2 is-cta-heading\">Get clear, confident legal advice today</h2></div></div><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-medium\"><p class=\"text-size-medium\">We’re here to help you take your next step with confidence.</p></div><div class=\"button-group\"><a arrow-rotate=\"trigger\" data-btn-hover=\"\" data-theme=\"primary\" href=\"tel:+441132070000\" class=\"btn is-icon w-inline-block\"><div class=\"btn__bg\"></div><div class=\"btn__circle-wrap\"><div class=\"btn__circle\"><div class=\"before__100\"></div></div></div><div class=\"btn__text\"><p class=\"btn-text-p\">Call us today</p></div><div btn-arrow=\"right\" class=\"arrow is-button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-xsmall 